    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the onion is softening, chop your <strong>cherry</strong> <strong>tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>paste</strong> and <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>stock</strong> <strong>mix</strong> in 225ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[390ml] </span><strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1692958199380-x200.jpg",
