            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>fresh</strong> <strong>tagliatelle</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the tagliatelle for 3-4 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>tagliatelle</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>salad</strong> and <strong>balsamic</strong> <strong>vinegar</strong> in a bowl with a drizzle of<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong> - this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
